data.description: Immerse yourself in the pinnacle of comfortable living within this exquisite 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, perfectly situated in the coveted Diamondhead neighborhood. Step through the inviting entrance into a luminous and expansive living space featuring captivating brick floors, a warm fireplace, and lofty ceilings that amplify the overall feeling of openness. The intelligently crafted split floor plan ensures tranquility, with the primary bedroom gracefully secluded from the other two bedrooms. Outside, a spacious fenced yard sets the stage for memorable outdoor gatherings, complemented by the convenience of abundant RV parking space. Enjoy a wealth of amenities as a resident, including access to 3 swimming pools, tennis courts, and pickleball facilities. Revel in the delights of luxurious living and embrace the vibrant golf community lifestyle in this remarkable Diamondhead gem.
